### AI Gateway — provider routing + model health
# Internal endpoint'ler için X-Internal-Key gerekir.

### Provider listesi
GET {{aiGateway}}/providers
X-Internal-Key: {{gatewayInternalKey}}

###

### Provider health (her birinin durumu)
GET {{aiGateway}}/providers/status
X-Internal-Key: {{gatewayInternalKey}}

###

### Available models
GET {{aiGateway}}/models
X-Internal-Key: {{gatewayInternalKey}}

###

### Quick chat completion (test)
POST {{aiGateway}}/v1/chat/completions
Content-Type: application/json
X-Internal-Key: {{gatewayInternalKey}}

{
  "model": "ollama/llama3.2:3b",
  "messages": [
    { "role": "user", "content": "Say hello in Turkish in one short sentence." }
  ],
  "max_tokens": 50
}

###

### Embedding test
POST {{aiGateway}}/v1/embeddings
Content-Type: application/json
X-Internal-Key: {{gatewayInternalKey}}

{
  "model": "ollama/nomic-embed-text",
  "input": "Test cümlesi"
}

###
